('Vitriolic Sphere',4,'Evocation','Action','150 feet','Instantaneous','V, S, M (drop of bile)','Sorcerer, Wizard','A glowing acid ball explodes in a 20-foot Sphere. Dexterity saves: 10d4 Acid on fail + 5d4 Acid at end of next turn; half initial damage only on success. Higher Slots: +2d4 initial per slot above 4.',false,false),
('Wall of Fire',4,'Evocation','Action','120 feet','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S, M (charcoal)','Druid, Sorcerer, Wizard','A wall (up to 60 ft long, 20 ft high, 1 ft thick, or ring 20 ft diameter). When created: Dexterity save, 5d8 Fire on fail. One chosen side deals 5d8 Fire to creatures ending turn within 10 ft. Higher Slots: +1d8 per slot above 4.',false,true),
('Wall of Force',5,'Evocation','Action','120 feet','Concentration, up to 10 minutes','V, S, M (shard of glass)','Wizard','An Invisible wall (up to ten 10x10 ft panels, or hemispherical dome/globe up to 10-ft radius). Immune to all damage. Can''t be dispelled by Dispel Magic. Disintegrate destroys it. Extends into the Ethereal Plane.',false,true),
('Wall of Ice',6,'Evocation','Action','120 feet','Concentration, up to 10 minutes','V, S, M (piece of quartz)','Wizard','A 1-foot-thick ice wall (up to ten 10-ft squares, or hemispherical dome/globe 10-ft radius). Creation: Dexterity save, 10d6 Cold on fail. AC 12, 30 HP per 10-ft section. Destroyed sections leave frigid air: 5d6 Cold on failed Constitution save. Higher Slots: +2d6 wall damage, +1d6 frigid air per slot above 6.',false,true),
('Wall of Stone',5,'Evocation','Action','120 feet','Concentration, up to 10 minutes','V, S, M (granite cube)','Druid, Sorcerer, Wizard','A nonmagical stone wall (6 inches thick, up to ten 10x10-ft panels or twenty 10x20-ft 3-inch-thick panels). Must merge with existing stone. Full duration Concentration = permanent.',false,true),
('Wall of Thorns',6,'Conjuration','Action','120 feet','Concentration, up to 10 minutes','V, S, M (handful of thorns)','Druid','A wall of thorny brush (up to 60 ft long, 10 ft high, 5 ft thick, or circle 20 ft diameter, 20 ft high). Blocks line of sight. Creation: 7d8 Piercing on failed Dexterity save. Moving through costs 4 ft per foot. First time entering or ending turn in wall each turn: Dexterity save, 7d8 Slashing on fail. Higher Slots: +1d8 both per slot above 6.',false,true),
('Warding Bond',2,'Abjuration','Action','Touch','1 hour','V, S, M (pair of platinum rings 50+ GP each, both worn)','Cleric, Paladin','A mystic connection: target within 60 ft gains +1 AC and saving throws, Resistance to all damage. You take the same damage as the target. Ends if either of you drops to 0 HP, you are 60+ ft apart, or the spell is recast.',false,false),
('Water Breathing',3,'Transmutation','Action or Ritual','30 feet','24 hours','V, S, M (short reed)','Druid, Ranger, Sorcerer, Wizard','Up to ten willing creatures can breathe underwater while retaining their normal respiration.',true,false),
('Water Walk',3,'Transmutation','Action or Ritual','30 feet','1 hour','V, S, M (piece of cork)','Cleric, Druid, Ranger, Sorcerer','Up to ten willing creatures can move across liquid surfaces as if solid ground (lava heat still applies). Bonus Action to move between surface and liquid.',true,false),
('Web',2,'Conjuration','Action','60 feet','Concentration, up to 1 hour','V, S, M (spiderweb)','Sorcerer, Wizard','A 20-foot Cube of sticky webbing (Difficult Terrain, Lightly Obscured). Must be anchored. First time entering or starting turn there: Dexterity save or Restrained. Strength (Athletics) vs. your DC to escape. Flammable.',false,true),
('Weird',9,'Illusion','Action','120 feet','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S','Warlock, Wizard','Each chosen creature in a 30-foot Sphere makes Wisdom save: 10d10 Psychic + Frightened on fail, half on success. Frightened creature makes Wisdom save at end of each turn: fail = 5d10 Psychic; success = spell ends for it.',false,true),
('Wind Walk',6,'Transmutation','1 minute','30 feet','8 hours','V, S, M (candle)','Druid','You and up to ten willing creatures assume gaseous form: Fly Speed 300 ft (hover), Immunity to Prone, Resistance to Bludgeoning/Piercing/Slashing. Only Dash or Magic action (begin reverting, takes 1 minute, Stunned during).',false,false),
('Wind Wall',3,'Evocation','Action','120 feet','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S, M (fan and feather)','Druid, Ranger','A wall of strong wind (up to 50 ft long, 15 ft high, 1 ft thick). Strength saves: 4d8 Bludgeoning on fail. Blocks gas and Small+ flying creatures. Deflects arrows and bolts.',false,true),
('Wish',9,'Conjuration','Action','Self','Instantaneous','V','Sorcerer, Wizard','The mightiest mortal spell. Basic use: duplicate any spell of level 8 or lower. Alternatively: Object Creation, Instant Health (20 creatures regain all HP), Resistance (10 creatures permanent Resistance), Spell Immunity, Sudden Learning (replace a feat), Roll Redo, or Reshape Reality (DM discretion). Non-duplicate use: 1d10 Necrotic per spell level until Long Rest, Strength 3 for 2d4 days, 33% chance to never cast Wish again.',false,false),
('Witch Bolt',1,'Evocation','Action','60 feet','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S, M (lightning-struck twig)','Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard','Ranged spell attack: 2d12 Lightning on hit. Bonus Action on later turns to deal 1d12 Lightning automatically. Ends if target leaves range or has Total Cover. Higher Slots: +1d12 initial per slot above 1.',false,true),
('Word of Radiance',0,'Evocation','Action','Self','Instantaneous','V, M (sunburst token)','Cleric','Radiance erupts in a 5-foot Emanation. Chosen creatures make Constitution saves or take 1d6 Radiant. Cantrip Upgrade: +1d6 at levels 5, 11, 17.',false,false),
('Word of Recall',6,'Conjuration','Action','5 feet','Instantaneous','V','Cleric','You and up to five willing creatures within 5 ft instantly teleport to a previously designated sanctuary. Must designate a location by casting this spell there first.',false,false),
('Wrathful Smite',1,'Necromancy','Bonus Action (after hitting)','Self','1 minute','V','Paladin','The target takes +1d6 Necrotic. Wisdom save or Frightened. Frightened target repeats save at end of each turn to end. Higher Slots: +1d6 per slot above 1.',false,false),
('Yolande''s Regal Presence',5,'Enchantment','Action','Self','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S, M (miniature tiara)','Bard, Wizard','Unearthly majesty in a 10-foot Emanation. Creatures entering or ending turn there make Wisdom saves: 4d6 Psychic + Prone + pushed 10 ft on fail, half on success (once per turn).',false,true),
('Zone of Truth',2,'Enchantment','Action','60 feet','10 minutes','V, S','Bard, Cleric, Paladin','A 15-foot Sphere against deception. Creatures entering or starting turn there make Charisma saves: fail = can''t speak deliberate lies. You know whether each creature succeeds or fails.',false,false)
,('Alustriel''s Mooncloak',5,'Abjuration','Action','Self','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S, M (moonstone 50+ GP)','Bard, Druid, Ranger, Wizard','Moonlight fills a 20-foot Emanation (Dim Light). You and allies have Half Cover and Resistance to Cold, Lightning, and Radiant damage. End the spell to use Liberation (Reaction to succeed on a failed save vs Frightened/Grappled/Restrained) or Respite (Magic action, regain 4d10+mod HP for you or an ally).',false,true),
('Backlash',4,'Abjuration','Reaction (when taking damage)','60 feet','Instantaneous','V','Bard, Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard','Reduce the triggering damage by 4d6+mod. If from a creature within range, that creature makes Constitution save: 4d6 Force on fail, half on success. Higher Slots: damage reduction and Force damage each +1d6 per slot above 4.',false,false),
('Blade of Disaster',9,'Conjuration','Bonus Action','60 feet','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S','Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard','A 3-foot blade-shaped planar rift appears. Immediately and as Bonus Action on later turns: up to two melee spell attacks against creatures or objects within 5 ft (10d6 Force each; Critical Hit on 18+). Move the rift up to 60 ft as Bonus Action. Passes harmlessly through all barriers including Wall of Force.',false,true),
('Cacophonic Shield',3,'Evocation','Action','Self','Concentration, up to 10 minutes','V, S','Bard, Sorcerer, Wizard','Thunderous reverberations fill a 10-foot Emanation. Creatures entering or ending turns there make Constitution saves: 3d6 Thunder + Deafened until your next turn on fail, half on success. You have Resistance to Thunder; ranged attacks against you have Disadvantage. Higher Slots: +1d6 per slot above 3.',false,true),
('Conjure Constructs',3,'Conjuration','Action','60 feet','Concentration, up to 10 minutes','V, S, M (brass cog)','Wizard','A group of orderly spirits appears. Magic action to target a creature or object within 5 ft: Clockwork Force (3d6 Force on failed Dexterity save) or Orderly Ward (1d6+mod Temp HP). Move spirits 30 ft when you move. Higher Slots: +1d6 both per slot above 3.',false,true),
('Death Armor',2,'Necromancy','Action','Touch','1 hour','V, S, M (onyx 50+ GP, consumed)','Sorcerer, Wizard','An inky aura surrounds a touched creature. Advantage on Death Saving Throws. Once per turn, creatures hitting the target with a melee attack within 5 ft take 2d4 Necrotic.',false,false),
('Deryan''s Helpful Homunculi',2,'Conjuration','Action or Ritual','Self','8 hours','V, S, M (powdered gemstones 100+ GP and Artisan''s Tools, both consumed)','Cleric, Wizard','Summon helpful intangible spirits as homunculi with proficiency in Arcana and the Artisan''s Tools used. If crafting, they function as a single assistant, halving crafting time.',true,false),
('Dirge',6,'Enchantment','Action','Self','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V','Bard, Cleric','Deathly power fills a 60-foot Emanation. Designated creatures can''t regain HP while inside. Others make Constitution saves: 3d10 Necrotic + Prone on fail; half damage + Speed halved on success. As a Circle spell (min. 2 secondary casters, each expending level 4+ slot): duration up to 10 min; failed targets also gain 1 Exhaustion and can''t recover HP or reduce Exhaustion via Long Rest.',false,true),
('Doomtide',4,'Conjuration','Action','120 feet','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S, M (soot and dried eel)','Bard, Cleric, Warlock','A 20-foot Sphere of magical Darkness. Creatures inside make Wisdom saves: 5d6 Psychic + -1d6 to saves until end of next turn on fail, half on success. Sphere moves 10 ft from you each turn. As a Circle spell (min. 5 secondary casters, each expending level 3+ slot; requires three black pearls from Pandemonium, consumed): range 1 mile, duration until dispelled, no Concentration.',false,true),
('Elminster''s Effulgent Spheres',6,'Evocation','Action','Self','1 hour','V, S, M (opal 1,000+ GP)','Druid, Sorcerer, Wizard','Six chromatic spheres orbit you. Expend spheres for: Absorb Energy (Reaction when taking Acid/Cold/Fire/Lightning/Thunder damage, gain Resistance to that type until your next turn) or Energy Blast (Bonus Action, ranged spell attack, 3d6 damage of that type on hit; sphere expended regardless). Ends when no spheres remain. Higher Slots: +1 sphere per slot above 6.',false,false),
('Elminster''s Elusion',2,'Abjuration','Bonus Action','Self','Concentration, up to 10 minutes','V, S','Wizard','Advantage on saving throws against spells and magical effects. If you succeed on a half-damage save, you take no damage instead.',false,true),
('Holy Star of Mystra',8,'Evocation','Bonus Action','Self','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S','Cleric, Wizard','A glowing mote hovers above you (Bright Light 5 ft). Bonus Action: ranged spell attack vs a target within 120 ft, 4d10+mod Force or Radiant on hit. While active: Three-Quarters Cover; if you succeed on a save against a level 7 or lower spell targeting only you (no area of effect), Reaction to deflect it back at the caster using the caster''s own spell save DC.',false,true),
('Homunculus Servant',2,'Conjuration','1 hour or Ritual','10 feet','Instantaneous','V, S, M (gem 100+ GP)','Artificer','Summon a special Tiny Construct homunculus. It obeys your commands, shares your Initiative (acts after yours), and has Force Strike (melee or ranged, 1d6+spell level Force) and Evasion. Higher Slots: use slot level in the stat block.',true,false),
('Laeral''s Silver Lance',3,'Evocation','Action','Self','Instantaneous','V, S, M (silver pin 250+ GP)','Cleric, Sorcerer, Wizard','Silver energy bursts in a 120-foot-long, 5-foot-wide Line. Chosen creatures make Strength saves: 3d10 Force + Prone on fail, half on success. Higher Slots: +1d10 per slot above 3.',false,false),
('Simbul''s Synostodweomer',7,'Transmutation','Action','Touch','1 hour','V, S','Sorcerer, Wizard','A touched creature regains HP whenever it casts a spell using a spell slot: roll unexpended Hit Point Dice equal to the slot''s level, regain that total + your spellcasting modifier. Those dice are expended.',false,false),
('Songal''s Elemental Suffusion',5,'Transmutation','Action','Self','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S, M (pearl 100+ GP)','Druid, Sorcerer, Wizard','Elemental Immunity (Resistance to one chosen type: Acid/Cold/Fire/Lightning/Thunder); Elemental Pulse (15-foot Emanation: 2d6 damage on failed Dexterity save + Prone, half on success; when cast and start of each turn); Flight (Fly Speed 30 ft, hover). As a Circle spell: up to 9 additional creatures gain benefits (each secondary caster expends level 2+ slot).',false,true),
('Spellfire Flare',1,'Evocation','Action','60 feet','Instantaneous','V, S','Sorcerer, Wizard','Ranged spell attack (target gains no benefit from Half or Three-Quarters Cover): 2d10 Radiant on hit. Higher Slots: one additional blast per slot above 1; separate attack roll for each.',false,false),
('Spellfire Storm',4,'Evocation','Action','60 feet','Concentration, up to 1 minute','V, S','Sorcerer, Wizard','A pillar of spellfire in a 20-foot-radius, 20-foot-high Cylinder (Bright Light). Constitution saves: 4d10 Radiant on fail, half on success. Creatures casting spells inside also make Constitution saves: fail = spell dissipates. As a Circle spell (requires blue star sapphire 25,000+ GP, consumed; each secondary caster expends level 3+ slot): range 1 mile, no Concentration; area/duration scales with secondary caster count. Higher Slots: +1d10 per slot above 4.',false,true),
('Syluné''s Viper',3,'Conjuration','Bonus Action','Self','1 hour','V, S, M (snake fang)','Druid, Wizard','Gain 15 Temp HP (spell ends if none left). While active: Climb Speed = Speed; Venomous Bite (Magic action, ranged spell attack 50 ft, 1d6 Force on hit + Poisoned until start of your next turn; while Poisoned, target also has Incapacitated condition). Higher Slots: +5 Temp HP and +1d6 Venomous Bite damage per slot above 3.',false,false),
('Wardaway',1,'Abjuration','Action','60 feet','Instantaneous','V, S, M (miniature clay hand)','Bard, Cleric, Paladin, Wizard','One creature makes Constitution save (Constructs and Undead auto-succeed). Fail: 2d4 Force + Speed halved until your next turn + on its next turn can take only an action or Bonus Action (not both). Success: half damage only. Higher Slots: +2d4 per slot above 1.',false,false)
